OL,6,FA "thug" who left his victim needing
OL,7,Freconstructive surgery after a drunken
OL,8,Fattack has been banned from every pub
OL,9,Fin the country.
OL,11,FPaul Ormond, of Carolgate, Retford,
OL,12,Fcarried out an unprovoked assault
OL,13,Fafter a day of drinking in the Turks
OL,14,FHead in Retford, Nottinghamshire, on 6
OL,15,FJuly last year.
OL,17,FHe punched the man in the head,
OL,18,Fleaving him with serious facial
OL,19,Ffractures to his eye, nose and cheeks
OL,20,Fwhich required multiple surgeries and
OL,21,Fplates in his face.
