OL,6,FOrmond pleaded guilty to causing
OL,7,Fgrievous bodily harm at Nottingham
OL,8,FCrown Court he was given a two-year
OL,9,Fsuspended prison sentence.
OL,11,FJudge Recorder Sprawson described him
OL,12,Fas a "drunken thug" and banned him
OL,13,Ffrom entering pubs in England and
OL,14,FWales for the next two years.
OL,16,FThe 38-year-old will also have to wear
OL,17,Fan alcohol monitoring tag for 120
OL,18,Fdays, which will measure his sweat
OL,19,Fevery 30 minutes to determine if he
OL,20,Fhas consumed alcohol.
