OL,6,FHe will have to carry out 120 hours of
OL,7,Funpaid work and pay #7,500 in
OL,8,Fcompensation to the victim.
OL,10,FThe court heard Ormond has previous
OL,11,Fconvictions for offences including
OL,12,Fwounding with intent, affray and
OL,13,Fassaulting a police officer.
OL,15,FPC Andrew Sansom, of Notttinghamshire
OL,16,FPolice, said: "This was a vicious
OL,17,Fattack which continues to have a
OL,18,Fsignificant impact on the victim to
OL,19,Fthis day.
